  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a non-stick pan over medium heat. Add coconut oil and saut\u00019e the minced garlic for 1 minute.",
    "Add sambal oelek and cook for another minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add kidney beans and stir to combine with the sambal mixture.",
    "Season with salt, black pepper, and a squeeze of lime juice.",
    "Meanwhile, toast the bread slices in a toaster or under the broiler.",
